Author: Michael Dubno
Author-email: michael@dubno.com
License: UNKNOWN
Description: # R2D7 Shade Controller Package
        
        Package to control R2D7 shades through an Ethernet adaptor
        using Python.
        
        # Example:
        
            from time import sleep
            from r2d7py import *
            
            hub = R2D7Hub( 'host.test.com', 4008 )
        
            # Address=1, Unit=2, shade traversal time=14.2
            shade = hub.shade( 1, 2, 14.2 )
        
            # Open the shade
            shade.open()
            sleep(15.)
        
            # Position the shade half way
            shade.position = 50.
            sleep(15.)
        
            # Close the interface
            hub.close()
        
